reviewText: A deranged individual, who was bullied for his appearance when he was a youth, grows up fixated on porn which he confuses with reality. Computer skilled in the extreme, he discovers the location of Girl House - the residence dorm of young ladies who show their wares online - and goes there to wreak havoc and revenge for an exaggerated slight.  Nothing more need be said. But, for those who like this kind of movie, you will not be disappointed with the action, mayhem, form of deadly dispatch, and conclusion. As an aside, I am always stunned at the speed of any killer in these types of films. Regardless of size and weight, what object they may be carrying, or even wounded, they run like the wind and somehow always catch up with their intended victim.  At least it adds a "comical note" to the blood saturated setting that we must watch even if we would rather look away.

I liked this movie from start to finish Ali Cobrin who was in American Reunion is in this & looks hot as ever. It kept my attention from start to finish. I like it enough to put it on my list of future purchases. I think every horror fan should check it out.

A surprise from start to finish. It starts off very basic as far as slasher films, but stay with it; as a slasher ,over for over 30 years i would easily say this is the best since the 80s. the acting is decent the killer is very creepy , its violent with lots of nudity and the "mrs wimp" survivor dose one thing that right that most girls in the 80s didn't do. No spoiler so i won't say but the ending is very satisfying . I don't know why i never herd of this film , it really deserves to find an audience it is really really good.
